itemage</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_ball.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Member</span><br>  Posts: 8<br> <font color=#FF9300>(2/9/03 8:49:57 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fscbnforum58570frm16.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=14.topic>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> darkness</span><hr size=1> A dark wind has begun to blow across the world. The ground slowly pulses and trembles at the arrival of an evil that had been thought destroyed. He claws his way out of his rocky tomb leaving a deep claw mark gashed into the dirt as he pulls himself from the grave that had trapped him for centeries. His eyes gleamed bright red as he inhaled again feeling the rush of fresh air serge through his body. He pulled himself to his feet and looked up the mountain side to see his superior officer. The one who let lose his power to reek havoc once more in this land of chaos. An evil grin slips across his face as he turns to the wilderness of the forest and that beyond. With a loud booming voice he spoke.<br>
<br>
"Creatures of the night. Beings of the Dark. All manners of EVIL! Heed my call! I have returned to reclaim our former glory! To plunge this world of Chaos back into a land of Darkness! Join me in reclaiming what is rightfully ours! <a href="http://www.kingsofchaos.com/page.php?id=266341" target="_new">JOIN MY ARMY</a> SO WE MAY TAKE BACK WHAT WAS TAKEN FROM US! JOIN MEEEE!!!"<br>
<br>
The creatures in the forest all went silent as the birds flew further from him. The woodland creatures were all hushed. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#F9FBFD><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub98.ezboard.com/bscbnforum58570.showUserPublicProfile?gid=stephencrowley>Stephen Crowley</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Member</span><br>  Posts: 169<br> <font color=#FF9300>(2/10/03 7:23:04 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fscbnforum58570frm16.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=14.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: darkness</span><hr size=1> Know, sir, that in time, the light can and will drive you back. Take heed, all who consider this man's offer. You accept it at your peril. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFFF><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub98.ezboard.com/bscbnforum58570.showUserPublicProfile?gid=midnitemage>midnitemage</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_ball.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Member</span><br>  Posts: 9<br> <font color=#FF9300>(2/10/03 10:10:01 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fscbnforum58570frm16.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=14.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: darkness</span><hr size=1> The only peril you face, sir, is opposing me. dont dare to think that you can stop my power.. My power will only grow with time... You dont begin to presume that you will be able to stop me. Just try... <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :evil --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/devil.gif ALT=":evil"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
-The Morbid Mage <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#F9FBFD><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub98.ezboard.com/bscbnforum58570.showUserPublicProfile?gid=stephencrowley>Stephen Crowley</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Member</span><br>  Posts: 170<br> <font color=#FF9300>(2/10/03 11:10:30 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fscbnforum58570frm16.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=14.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: darkness</span><hr size=1> You will find, sir, that there are lights which can never be extinguished, not even in the World of Darkness. Look deep inside my soul, and you will find such a light.   And compared to it, your power means absolutely nothiing.    <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFFF><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub98.ezboard.com/bscbnforum58570.showUserPublicProfile?gid=midnitemage>midnitemage</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_ball.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Member</span><br>  Posts: 10<br> <font color=#FF9300>(2/10/03 12:05:49 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fscbnforum58570frm16.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=14.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: darkness</span><hr size=1> Oh how blissful you must feel to be so ignorant. You must know that light cannot exist without darkness as well as the other way around. I have been present for days untold. I have done and experienced things that you cannot even begin to phathom. You say you hold the light that can hold back my wave of utter darkness? Then show me... Show me that you can repel my evil. Try to divert my enless anguish and tourment. Then when your soul is ripped from your body and burnt to ash, I will be there to claim you as another one of my soldiars of darkness. Make you a wraith of devostation. I becon you to face me whelp. Then you will know true fear. I will show you what hell let loose upon this world really looks like.<br>
<br>
-The Morbid Mage<br>
<br>
(hehe. this is fun.. if any of you have clicked on the links on my first post, it leads you to a funny lil game of war. hence the whole join my army thing. ^_^ jus for clerifaction.. if possible, can everyone just click on it once? and if you are really nice, can you click on it once a day? that is all i ask. Just click one single time. thanks. -Yoshi) <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#F9FBFD><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub98.ezboard.com/bscbnforum58570.showUserPublicProfile?gid=stephencrowley>Stephen Crowley</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Member</span><br>  Posts: 171<br> <font color=#FF9300>(2/10/03 1:26:04 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fscbnforum58570frm16.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=14.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: darkness</span><hr size=1> Ignorance? You speak of ignorance, sir?<br>
<br>
Let me explain something to you. I have seen darkness greater than anything you could possibly imagine. I have stepped into the abyss, and despite my despair, pressed onward, first because I was driven by the ghosts of my past, and second there was something within me that refused to yield. After pushing onward, I saw an end to the tunnel in the distance.<br>
<br>
Do you know what I saw at the end, my friend? I saw light.<br>
<br>
It was then I learned that though darkness may come from without, light can and must come from within. <br>
<br>
You cannot extinguish the light, my friend. And as for the darkness, true the light needs it to exist, but is not the reverse also true?<br>
<br>
There will always be people like you who carry the darkness, sir. But wherever you go, there will always be people like me to turn you back.<br>
<br>
See you around.<br>
<br>
(LOL... Yoshi let's keep going even if it is OOC. And yes, I clicked your link. Amusing stuff.) <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFFF><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub98.ezboard.com/bscbnforum58570.showUserPublicProfile?gid=midnitemage>midnitemage</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_ball.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Member</span><br>  Posts: 11<br> <font color=#FF9300>(2/10/03 3:56:52 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fscbnforum58570frm16.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=14.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: darkness</span><hr size=1> People? You think I am one of your retched race? A pathetic HUMAN! Don't make me vomit!! Even the most wickid of your kind can't comprehend how deep and how absolute my power truely is. I am secure in the knowledge that my rule will be absolute. I am an entity of evil. I have no weakness. My power may only be equaled by a true god. My abilities are only limited by my summoner's imagination. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :evil --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/devil.gif ALT=":evil"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  I dare you to try and find out who that is. Do not speak as if you have been to the abyss. The true abyss is not within you. The true abyss is a combined contiousness of all living beings combining all their fears, woes, and sorrows. Walk their halls for merely a moment. Then I would like to see you walk out with such resolve. I have roamed those halls for longer than the oldest entity in this retched world. : pulls a hand of long, wretched, grotesque, looking claws. He brings them to his face in a fist, with his extended opposable claw ran the length of his chin and neck, resting his head on the hand.: But you have an interesting point. Why should my reign be absolute if there is light in this world? :he turns to look at you his eyes glowing bright red and as he spoke these last few words, the deepest and darkest feeling of despair flows through all who listen: Because you beings of the light have had this world long enough and balance must be restored.<br>
<br>
- The Morbid Mage <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#F9FBFD><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub98.ezboard.com/bscbnforum58570.showUserPublicProfile?gid=stephencrowley>Stephen Crowley</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Member</span><br>  Posts: 172<br> <font color=#FF9300>(2/10/03 4:20:03 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fscbnforum58570frm16.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=14.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: darkness</span><hr size=1> &gt;&gt;Because you beings of the light have had this world long enough and balance must be restored.&lt;&lt;<br>
<br>
Had this world, you say?<br>
<br>
Had this world?<br>
<br>
Let me further your education. I have seen the darkest side of humanity. I have seen petty bickering descend into blood feuds that have ripped this world asunder. I have seen brother turn on brother out of jealousy. I have bore witness as this world has turned on itself time and time again.<br>
<br>
I have seen your work, demon.<br>
<br>
And yet, I have seen acts of such sacrifice, of such sheer and overwhelming courage, of such noble cause and purpose, as to leave no doubt in my mind: The light will prevail.<br>
<br>
Speak to me not of darkness, demon. Dwell and hide in your tunnels, scheme and manipulate, use your abilities as you will.<br>
<br>
And when you emerge to show yourself, I will be there.<br>
<br>
And on that day, I will show you the value of a belief.<br>
<br>
(LOL. Ahhh... this is getting funny. Hope the rest of you aren't bored.) <br>
